title: Bracelet, 1850–75
creditline: Gift of the estate and in memory of Robert B. Noyes
description: Articulated bracelet with clasp; design of oval garnets set in frames with ornament belwo and bow knot above, alternating with round garnets and gold ornaments, bands engraved in leaf-design at either side of the bracelet.

tombstone.epitaph:
Bracelet, 1850–75.
1850–75. Gold, black enamel, garnets. Gift of the estate and in memory of Robert B. Noyes. 1946-50-2.
